text: Grafton Township is a township in Walsh County, North Dakota, United States. 51.1% (167) of the population are male, and the other 48.9% (160) are female. As of the 2010 census, the population of Grafton Township is 327. ==References== ==See also== *Walsh County, North Dakota Category:Townships in North Dakota Category:Townships in Walsh County, North Dakota
